description:
Dear MonetDB Developers,

I encountered an unexpected execution result. If you have the opportunity to take a look, I would greatly appreciate your time and efforts. Let's make MonetDB more robust!
```sql
CREATE TABLE t0(c0 INT);

INSERT INTO t0(c0) VALUES(82);

SELECT * FROM t0 WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM (VALUES (t0.c0)) WHERE TRUE);
-- Wrong Execution Result: 82
-- Expected Result: Empty result
```
